Pre-installation Instructions
=============================

	This installation requires the pre-installation of the cmake tool,
a C++ compiler, and the libraries: libdivsufsort and sdsl.
	
	For Linux, you can install libraries libdivsufsort and sdsl via

	 $ ./pre-install.sh 


Basic Instructions
==================

	The shell command 'make' should compile this program.

	After compilation the binary 'index' will be created in the working
directory, e.g. you can all it in this directory via
	
	$ ./index -t ../example/text.fa -z 8 -o output.txt
